<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>PlanIA — Assistente de Configuração</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#F9F8F5;--bg2:#F3F2EE;--ink:#0E0E0C;--ink2:#1C1C19;
  --muted:#6B6B63;--subtle:#9A9A90;--line:#E2E0D8;--line2:#D0CEC5;
  --amber:#C17F3A;--amber2:#E09A4E;--abg:#FDF6EC;--abd:#F0D9B5;
  --green:#1A7A4A;--gbg:#EBF7F1;--gbd:#A8DFBF;
  --blue:#2563EB;--bbg:#EFF4FF;--bbd:#BFDBFE;
  --red:#C0392B;--rbg:#FEF0EE;--rbd:#F5C6C2;
  --F:'Inter',sans-serif;--M:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:15px}
body{font-family:var(--F);background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;min-height:100vh;line-height:1.6}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--line2);border-radius:4px}

/* Layout */
.page{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 20px 80px}

/* Header */
.hdr{text-align:center;padding:48px 0 40px}
.hdr-logo{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:20px}
.logo-mark{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--ink);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.logo-icon{width:22px;height:22px;background:var(--amber);clip-path:polygon(50% 0%,100% 38%,82% 100%,18% 100%,0% 38%)}
.logo-name{font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.04em}
.logo-name em{color:var(--amber);font-style:normal}
.hdr-title{font-size:32px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.04em;margin-bottom:10px}
.hdr-sub{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.6}

/* Progress */
.progress{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:0;margin-bottom:40px}
.step-dot{
  width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .25s;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1;
}
.step-dot.done{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border:2px solid var(--green)}
.step-dot.active{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border:2px solid var(--ink);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(14,14,12,.12)}
.step-dot.idle{background:var(--bg);color:var(--muted);border:2px solid var(--line2)}
.step-line{flex:1;height:2px;background:var(--line);max-width:60px}
.step-line.done{background:var(--green)}

/* Cards */
.section{
  background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:16px;
  overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s;
}
.section.active{box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(14,14,12,.08);border-color:var(--line2)}
.section.done-card{border-color:var(--gbd);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gbg),#fff)}
.sec-head{
  padding:20px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
  cursor:pointer;user-select:none;
}
.sec-num{
  width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:12px;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;
}
.sec-num.active{background:var(--ink);color:#fff}
.sec-num.done{background:var(--green);color:#fff}
.sec-num.idle{background:var(--bg2);color:var(--muted);border:1px solid var(--line)}
.sec-info{flex:1}
.sec-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.03em}
.sec-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
.sec-status{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px}
.st-ok{background:var(--gbg);color:var(--green);border:1px solid var(--gbd)}
.st-pend{background:var(--bg2);color:var(--muted);border:1px solid var(--line)}
.st-req{background:var(--rbg);color:var(--red);border:1px solid var(--rbd)}

.sec-body{padding:0 24px 24px;display:none}
.sec-body.open{display:block}

/* Fields */
.field{margin-bottom:16px}
.field-label{
  font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);
  letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px;
}
.field-label span{color:var(--red);font-size:13px}
.field-hint{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.5}
.field-input{
  width:100%;background:var(--bg2);border:1.5px solid var(--line2);
  border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;
  font-size:13px;color:var(--ink);outline:none;
  transition:border-color .2s,background .2s;
  font-family:var(--M);
}
.field-input:focus{border-color:var(--amber);background:#fff}
.field-input::placeholder{color:var(--subtle);font-family:var(--F)}
.field-input.ok{border-color:var(--gbd);background:var(--gbg)}
.field-input.err-field{border-color:var(--rbd);background:var(--rbg)}

/* How-to box */
.howto{
  background:var(--bbg);border:1px solid var(--bbd);
  border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:16px;
}
.howto-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.howto ol{padding-left:18px}
.howto li{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:2px}
.howto li strong{color:var(--ink2);font-weight:600}
.howto a{color:var(--amber);font-weight:600}
.howto code{font-family:var(--M);background:rgba(37,99,235,.08);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px}

/* Warn box */
.warnbox{
  background:var(--abg);border:1px solid var(--abd);
  border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:14px;
  font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;gap:8px;
}
.warnbox-ico{flex-shrink:0;font-size:15px}

/* SQL block */
.sql-block{
  background:var(--ink);border-radius:10px;
  padding:16px;margin-bottom:14px;overflow-x:auto;
}
.sql-block pre{font-family:var(--M);font-size:11px;color:#A8FF78;line-height:1.7;white-space:pre}
.sql-copy{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
  border-radius:6px;padding:5px 12px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;
  cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s;margin-bottom:8px;display:inline-block;
}
.sql-copy:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.18)}

/* Buttons */
.btn-row{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:18px}
.btn{
  padding:11px 22px;border-radius:10px;border:none;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .2s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
}
.btn-primary{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,14,12,.2)}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--ink2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-amber{background:var(--amber);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(193,127,58,.3)}
.btn-amber:hover{background:var(--amber2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--line2);color:var(--muted)}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--line);color:var(--ink)}
.btn-green{background:var(--green);color:#fff}
.btn-green:hover{filter:brightness(1.1)}
.btn-big{padding:16px 36px;font-size:15px;border-radius:14px;width:100%;justify-content:center}

/* Test result */
.test-result{
  border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;margin-top:12px;
  font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;display:none;
}
.test-ok{background:var(--gbg);border:1px solid var(--gbd);color:var(--green)}
.test-err{background:var(--rbg);border:1px solid var(--rbd);color:var(--red)}
.test-result.show{display:block}

/* Final section */
.final-box{
  background:var(--ink);border-radius:20px;
  padding:40px;text-align:center;margin-top:20px;
}
.final-title{font-size:26px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.04em;color:#fff;margin-bottom:10px}
.final-sub{font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.6;max-width:460px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.final-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn-final-dl{background:var(--amber);color:#fff;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:12px;border:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.btn-final-dl:hover{background:var(--amber2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-final-adm{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);padding:14px 28px;border-radius:12px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.btn-final-adm:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2)}

/* File tabs */
.file-tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.ftab{
  padding:7px 14px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--line2);
  background:var(--bg2);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);
  cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
}
.ftab:hover{border-color:var(--line);color:var(--ink)}
.ftab.active{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-color:var(--ink)}
.ftab-icon{font-size:14px}

/* Deploy steps */
.deploy-steps{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-top:14px}
.ds{display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--line)}
.ds-n{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.ds-body{flex:1}
.ds-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:3px}
.ds-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.55}
.ds-link{color:var(--amber);font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}
.ds-link:hover{text-decoration:underline}

/* Tag */
.tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;border-radius:100px;padding:3px 10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700}
.tag-green{background:var(--gbg);color:var(--green);border:1px solid var(--gbd)}
.tag-amber{background:var(--abg);color:var(--amber);border:1px solid var(--abd)}
.tag-blue{background:var(--bbg);color:var(--blue);border:1px solid var(--bbd)}

/* Toast */
#toast{
  position:fixed;bottom:24px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-radius:12px;
  padding:12px 20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;
  box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
  display:none;z-index:999;white-space:nowrap;
  animation:toastIn .25s ease;
}
@keyframes toastIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}}

/* Spinner */
.spinner{width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);border-top-color:#fff;animation:spin .7s linear infinite;display:inline-block}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}

/* Divider */
.divider{height:1px;background:var(--line);margin:16px 0}

@media(max-width:600px){
  .hdr{padding:32px 0 28px}
  .hdr-title{font-size:24px}
  .sec-head{padding:16px 18px}
  .sec-body{padding:0 18px 18px}
  .final-box{padding:28px 20px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="toast"></div>

<div class="page">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="hdr">
    <div class="hdr-logo">
      <div class="logo-mark"><div class="logo-icon"></div></div>
      <span class="logo-name">Plan<em>IA</em></span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hdr-title">Assistente de Configuração</h1>
    <p class="hdr-sub">Preencha as informações abaixo e eu gero os arquivos prontos pra subir no servidor. Leva menos de 10 minutos!</p>
  </div>

  <!-- PROGRESS -->
  <div class="progress" id="progress">
    <div class="step-dot active" id="pd-1" onclick="goSection(1)">1</div>
    <div class="step-line" id="pl-1"></div>
    <div class="step-dot idle" id="pd-2" onclick="goSection(2)">2</div>
    <div class="step-line" id="pl-2"></div>
    <div class="step-dot idle" id="pd-3" onclick="goSection(3)">3</div>
    <div class="step-line" id="pl-3"></div>
    <div class="step-dot idle" id="pd-4" onclick="goSection(4)">4</div>
    <div class="step-line" id="pl-4"></div>
    <div class="step-dot idle" id="pd-5" onclick="goSection(5)">5</div>
    <div class="step-line" id="pl-5"></div>
    <div class="step-dot idle" id="pd-6" onclick="goSection(6)">🚀</div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── STEP 1: SUPABASE ── -->
  <div class="section active" id="sec-1">
    <div class="sec-head" onclick="toggleSec(1)">
      <div class="sec-num active" id="sn-1">1</div>
      <div class="sec-info">
        <div class="sec-title">🗄️ Supabase — Banco de dados</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">URL do projeto e chave pública</div>
      </div>
      <span class="sec-status st-req" id="ss-1">Obrigatório</span>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-body open" id="sb-1">

      <div class="howto">
        <div class="howto-title">📋 Como pegar as chaves do Supabase</div>
        <ol>
          <li>Acesse <a href="https://supabase.com" target="_blank"><strong>supabase.com</strong></a> e entre na sua conta</li>
          <li>Clique no seu projeto <strong>plania</strong></li>
          <li>No menu lateral clique em <strong>Settings → API</strong></li>
          <li>Copie o <strong>Project URL</strong> (começa com <code>https://</code>)</li>
          <li>Copie a chave <strong>anon public</strong> (começa com <code>eyJ...</code>)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="warnbox">
        <span class="warnbox-ico">⚠️</span>
        <span>Se ainda não criou o projeto no Supabase, <a href="https://supabase.com" target="_blank" style="color:var(--amber);font-weight:600">clique aqui</a> para criar. É gratuito. Após criar, rode o SQL do SETUP.md nas tabelas.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Project URL <span>*</span></div>
        <div class="field-hint">Formato: <code>https://xxxxxxxxxxxxx.supabase.co</code></div>
        <input class="field-input" id="f-sburl" type="url" placeholder="https://seuprojetoxyz.supabase.co" oninput="validateField(this,'sburl')"/>
        <div class="test-result" id="tr-sburl"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Chave anon public <span>*</span></div>
        <div class="field-hint">Começa com <code>eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...</code></div>
        <input class="field-input" id="f-sbanon" type="text" placeholder="eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..." oninput="validateField(this,'sbanon')"/>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">E-mail do administrador <span>*</span></div>
        <div class="field-hint">Seu e-mail que usou pra se cadastrar no Supabase — será o login do painel admin.</div>
        <input class="field-input" id="f-admin" type="email" placeholder="seuemail@gmail.com" oninput="validateField(this,'admin')"/>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="testSupabase()">
          <span>🔌</span> Testar conexão
        </button>
        <button class="btn btn-amber" onclick="nextSec(1)">
          Próximo →
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="test-result" id="tr-sb"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── STEP 2: ANTHROPIC ── -->
  <div class="section" id="sec-2">
    <div class="sec-head" onclick="toggleSec(2)">
      <div class="sec-num idle" id="sn-2">2</div>
      <div class="sec-info">
        <div class="sec-title">🤖 Anthropic — Inteligência Artificial</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Chave da API que gera os planos de estudo</div>
      </div>
      <span class="sec-status st-req" id="ss-2">Obrigatório</span>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-body" id="sb-2">

      <div class="howto">
        <div class="howto-title">📋 Como criar a API Key</div>
        <ol>
          <li>Acesse <a href="https://console.anthropic.com" target="_blank"><strong>console.anthropic.com</strong></a></li>
          <li>Faça login ou crie sua conta</li>
          <li>Vá em <strong>API Keys → Create Key</strong></li>
          <li>Dê um nome (ex: <code>plania-producao</code>) e clique em <strong>Create</strong></li>
          <li>Copie a chave agora — ela começa com <code>sk-ant-</code> e <strong>não aparece de novo</strong></li>
          <li>Adicione crédito em <strong>Billing → Add credits</strong> (mínimo $5 USD)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="warnbox">
        <span class="warnbox-ico">🔒</span>
        <span>Nunca compartilhe esta chave. O custo é ~R$0,01 por plano gerado. Com $5 USD você gera mais de 5.000 planos.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">API Key da Anthropic <span>*</span></div>
        <div class="field-hint">Começa com <code>sk-ant-api03-</code> ou <code>sk-ant-</code></div>
        <input class="field-input" id="f-apikey" type="text" placeholder="sk-ant-api03-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX" oninput="validateField(this,'apikey')"/>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="testAnthropicKey()">
          <span>🧪</span> Verificar formato
        </button>
        <button class="btn btn-amber" onclick="nextSec(2)">Próximo →</button>
      </div>
      <div class="test-result" id="tr-api"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── STEP 3: CAKTO ── -->
  <div class="section" id="sec-3">
    <div class="sec-head" onclick="toggleSec(3)">
      <div class="sec-num idle" id="sn-3">3</div>
      <div class="sec-info">
        <div class="sec-title">💳 Cakto — Pagamentos</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Link de checkout do produto R$21,90/mês</div>
      </div>
      <span class="sec-status st-pend" id="ss-3">Opcional</span>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-body" id="sb-3">

      <div class="howto">
        <div class="howto-title">📋 Como pegar o link do Cakto</div>
        <ol>
          <li>Acesse <a href="https://cakto.com.br" target="_blank"><strong>cakto.com.br</strong></a> e entre na sua conta</li>
          <li>Vá em <strong>Meus Produtos</strong> e clique no PlanIA Premium</li>
          <li>Clique em <strong>Checkout</strong> ou <strong>Compartilhar</strong></li>
          <li>Copie o link (formato: <code>pay.cakto.com.br/XXXXXXXX</code>)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="warnbox">
        <span class="warnbox-ico">💡</span>
        <span>Se ainda não criou no Cakto, deixe em branco por enquanto. O botão de assinar vai redirecionar pro seu WhatsApp automaticamente.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Link de checkout Cakto</div>
        <div class="field-hint">Formato: <code>https://pay.cakto.com.br/XXXXXXXX</code></div>
        <input class="field-input" id="f-cakto" type="url" placeholder="https://pay.cakto.com.br/seu-link"/>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="nextSec(3)">Pular por agora</button>
        <button class="btn btn-amber" onclick="nextSec(3)">Próximo →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── STEP 4: WHATSAPP ── -->
  <div class="section" id="sec-4">
    <div class="sec-head" onclick="toggleSec(4)">
      <div class="sec-num idle" id="sn-4">4</div>
      <div class="sec-info">
        <div class="sec-title">📱 WhatsApp — Suporte e vendas</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Seu número para receber mensagens de alunos</div>
      </div>
      <span class="sec-status st-req" id="ss-4">Obrigatório</span>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-body" id="sb-4">

      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Número do WhatsApp <span>*</span></div>
        <div class="field-hint">Com DDI (55) + DDD + número. Sem espaços, traços ou parênteses. Exemplo: <code>5553999887766</code></div>
        <input class="field-input" id="f-wa" type="tel" placeholder="5553999887766" oninput="validateField(this,'wa')" maxlength="13"/>
        <div class="test-result" id="tr-wa"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="warnbox">
        <span class="warnbox-ico">📲</span>
        <span>Este número aparece nos botões de suporte do site e no botão de WhatsApp flutuante. Use um número que você responde com frequência.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-amber" onclick="nextSec(4)">Próximo →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── STEP 5: SENHA ADMIN ── -->
  <div class="section" id="sec-5">
    <div class="sec-head" onclick="toggleSec(5)">
      <div class="sec-num idle" id="sn-5">5</div>
      <div class="sec-info">
        <div class="sec-title">🔐 Senha do painel admin</div>
